## Integration with Auto-Flow

### During STEP 6 (Evaluation)
The Evaluation AI checks each security item as part of the **Security** scoring category (15% weight). Any critical security issue results in an automatic FAIL regardless of other scores.

### During STEP 8 (PR Review)
The PR template includes this checklist. The PR author must check each applicable item before requesting review.

### CI Integration
Consider adding automated security checks to CI:
- **SAST**: Static analysis (e.g., Semgrep, CodeQL)
- **SCA**: Dependency scanning (e.g., Dependabot, Snyk)
- **Secret scanning**: Detect committed secrets (e.g., GitGuardian, truffleHog)
